[DhtmlXQ_comment15]As can be seen from the diagram, red's P3+1 has been the move that has been played very often by red players.||In the past, red tried P7+1 but statistical evidence would show that black would be able to do well in that variation and that is why it has gradually fallen out of favor.[/DhtmlXQ_comment15]
