[DhtmlXQ_comment27]This is a less violent, more stable choice from red. Red decides to change his formation to allow for better defense.||If red chose to attack with C8-1, black would sacrifice material to have an attack.||Red would also gain material if he accepted black's sacrifice with R7+3 but black's ensuing attack would be seething.　[/DhtmlXQ_comment27]
